#: app/templates/faq.html:7
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "常见问题"

#: app/templates/faq.html:8
msgid "Quick answers to common visitor, artist, and submission questions."
msgstr "快速解答访客、艺术家和投稿相关的常见问题。"

#: app/templates/faq.html:23
msgid "How long does it take to receive a reply?"
msgstr "多久可以收到回复？"

#: app/templates/faq.html:28
msgid ""
"We usually respond within 1 to 2 business days. Messages sent outside "
"office hours are handled on the next working day."
msgstr "我们通常会在 1 到 2 个工作日内回复。非办公时间发送的消息将在下一个工作日处理。"

#: app/templates/faq.html:35
msgid "What should I include in an artwork submission?"
msgstr "作品提交时应包含哪些内容？"

#: app/templates/faq.html:40
msgid ""
"Please include your contact details, artwork title, medium, year, "
"description, and at least one clear image. A portfolio and CV/resume can "
"also be attached."
msgstr "请附上您的联系方式、作品标题、媒介、创作年份、作品描述，以及至少一张清晰图片。也可以附上作品集和简历。"

#: app/templates/faq.html:47
msgid "Can I contact the gallery about partnerships or events?"
msgstr "我可以就合作或活动事宜联系画廊吗？"

#: app/templates/faq.html:52
msgid ""
"Yes. Choose the partnership, collaboration, or events option in the "
"contact form and include the relevant dates, audience, and proposal "
"details."
msgstr "可以。请在联系表单中选择合作、联名或活动选项，并填写相关日期、受众和提案细节。"

