msgstr "谢谢您"

#: app/templates/thank_you.html:8
msgid "Your enquiry has been received."
msgstr "我们已收到您的咨询。"

#: app/templates/thank_you.html:21
msgid "We will be in touch soon"
msgstr "我们会尽快与您联系"

#: app/templates/thank_you.html:22
msgid ""
"Thank you for contacting Global Art Gallery. Our team reviews enquiries "
"during business hours and usually replies within 1 to 2 business days."
msgstr "感谢您联系全球艺术画廊。我们的团队会在办公时间处理咨询，通常会在 1 到 2 个工作日内回复。"

#: app/templates/thank_you.html:23
msgid ""
"If your question is urgent, you can also contact us by phone during our "
"office hours or use the resources below."
msgstr "如果您的问题较为紧急，也可以在办公时间拨打电话联系我们，或使用下面的资源。"

